tle": "汽车轮胎缓慢漏气怎么办？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1088057", "created": 1731152023, "deleted": 0, "content": "汽车右边前轮从某一天开始就缓慢的漏气，大概是一个星期漏 20 （ 220->200 ），去修车店里面看他说没有看到有漏气的地方😂。车平时很少开出去，一周基本只有周末会开车出去玩一下。\r\n\r\n这种问题怎么排查啊，各位 V 友有没有经验的提供一些建议，我自己看了几个星期没啥头绪，每个星期只能加气之后再出门。", "content_rendered": "<p>汽车右边前轮从某一天开始就缓慢的漏气，大概是一个星期漏 20 （ 220-&gt;200 ），去修车店里面看他说没有看到有漏气的地方😂。车平时很少开出去，一周基本只有周末会开车出去玩一下。</p>\n<p>这种问题怎么排查啊，各位 V 友有没有经验的提供一些建议，我自己看了几个星期没啥头绪，每个星期只能加气之后再出门。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1731152023, "replies": 33, "id": 1088057}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 27248, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3062, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 285041, "username": "lazydog", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lazydog", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e945/fa50/285041_mini.png?m=1730380860", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e945/fa50/285041_normal.png?m=1730380860", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e945/fa50/285041_large.png?m=1730380860", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e945/fa50/285041_xlarge.png?m=1730380860", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e945/fa50/285041_xlarge.png?m=1730380860", "created": 1516525524, "last_modified": 1730380860}, "last_reply_by": "winglight2016", "last_touched": 1731216320, "title": "京东国际日版 iPhone16 的